description:
Finally got the Invidia Gemini catbacks installed on my Infiniti Q50. Its everything I remember it being when I had it on my G37. Quiet and understated at idle, but deep, throaty, and aggressive VQ music under load.

Get it here for a Q50:
https://amzn.to/3d2lMyE

Get it here for a G37:
https://amzn.to/3ffP2oi

BUY ME A COFFEE/BEER:
https://www.buymeacoffee.com/squarewheels

HIT ME ON IG:
https://www.instagram.com/squarewheelsauto

Email for enquiries:
rob@squarewheelsauto.com

Listen to this awesome exhaust recorded under various conditions: 
0:00 Intro
0:24 Cold start & warm-up
1:07 Revs to 3k from idle
1:33 Idle from outside vs in-cabin
1:48 Driving around & a few pulls
5:24 Outside: Rolls & fly-by
6:05 Police/lurker mode
6:55 More rolls

Square Wheels Auto
#squarewheels #squarewheelsauto
